# Scripting & Automation Lab

## Commands & Concepts Learned
- Bash scripts (`.sh`)
- chmod +x to make scripts executable
- echo for output
- Variables ($NAME, $(command))
- Conditional statements (`if-else`)
- Loops (`for`)
- Running scripts `./script.sh`

## Key Learnings
- Scripts automate repetitive tasks
- Variables store data
- Conditional statements and loops add logic
- Scripts can combine multiple commands
